9/* memory type/access flags, do not match hardware values */
10#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_RO 1
11#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_WO 2
12#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_RW (NV_MEM_ACCESS_RO | NV_MEM_ACCESS_WO)
13#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_SYS 4
14#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_VM 8
15#define NV_MEM_ACCESS_NOSNOOP 16
16
17#define NV_MEM_TARGET_VRAM 0
18#define NV_MEM_TARGET_PCI 1
19#define NV_MEM_TARGET_PCI_NOSNOOP 2
20#define NV_MEM_TARGET_VM 3
21#define NV_MEM_TARGET_GART 4
22
23#define NVKM_RAM_TYPE_VM 0x7f
24#define NV_MEM_COMP_VM 0x03
25
26struct nvkm_mem {
27 struct drm_device *dev;
28
29 struct nvkm_vma bar_vma;
30 struct nvkm_vma vma[2];
31 u8 page_shift;
32
33 struct nvkm_mm_node *tag;
34 struct list_head regions;
35#ifdef __NetBSD__
36 bus_dmamap_t pages;
37#else
38 dma_addr_t *pages;
39#endif
40 u32 memtype;
41 u64 offset;
42 u64 size;
43 struct sg_table *sg;
44};
45
46struct nvkm_fb_tile {
47 struct nvkm_mm_node *tag;
48 u32 addr;
49 u32 limit;
50 u32 pitch;
51 u32 zcomp;
52};
53
54struct nvkm_fb {
55 const struct nvkm_fb_func *func;
56 struct nvkm_subdev subdev;
57
58 struct nvkm_ram *ram;
59
60 struct {
61 struct nvkm_fb_tile region[16];
62 int regions;
63 } tile;
64};

100struct nvkm_ram_data {
101 struct list_head head;
102 struct nvbios_ramcfg bios;
103 u32 freq;
104};
105
106enum nvkm_ram_type {
107 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_UNKNOWN = 0,
108 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_STOLEN,
109 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_SGRAM,
110 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_SDRAM,
111 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR1,
112 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR2,
113 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR3,
114 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR2,
115 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR3,
116 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR4,
117 NVKM_RAM_TYPE_GDDR5
118};
119
120struct nvkm_ram {
121 const struct nvkm_ram_func *func;
122 struct nvkm_fb *fb;
123 enum nvkm_ram_type type;
124 u64 size;
125
126#define NVKM_RAM_MM_SHIFT 12
127 struct nvkm_mm vram;
128 struct nvkm_mm tags;
129 u64 stolen;
130
131 int ranks;
132 int parts;
133 int part_mask;
134
135 u32 freq;
136 u32 mr[16];
137 u32 mr1_nuts;
138
139 struct nvkm_ram_data *next;
140 struct nvkm_ram_data former;
141 struct nvkm_ram_data xition;
142 struct nvkm_ram_data target;
143};
144
145struct nvkm_ram_func {
146 void *(*dtor)(struct nvkm_ram *);
147 int (*init)(struct nvkm_ram *);
148
149 int (*get)(struct nvkm_ram *, u64 size, u32 align, u32 size_nc,
150 u32 type, struct nvkm_mem **);
151 void (*put)(struct nvkm_ram *, struct nvkm_mem **);
152
153 int (*calc)(struct nvkm_ram *, u32 freq);
154 int (*prog)(struct nvkm_ram *);
155 void (*tidy)(struct nvkm_ram *);
156};
